{"type": "article", "id": 29773, "title": "模块型书架", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-18T22:47:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 61, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160718211438itvAElsPwVz3RCHG.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>墙面书架固然有着不错的收纳功能，但造型往往比较老套。最近 <a href=\"http://www.alemeacci-design.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alessandra Meacci</a> 推出的 <a href=\"http://www.alemeacci-design.com/#!slices/e6gk6\" rel=\"nofollow\">Slices</a> 系列书架则打破了传统的设计，采用了模块式面板的构造让人们可以在两片之间放上书本。远远看去这些立体书架就好像是一条条悬空游弋的鱼，仿佛将墙面改造成了“海底两万里”的舞台。Slices 的绿色版则被命名为“奇幻森林”，是一片绿油油的巨型龟背竹，作为墙饰同样有让人惊艳的效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718211502LJ2EgVZqwCzbkXvR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.963333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718211502NmsQJaorMbOPKn5q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.296667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718211503g4nU5ZSdCvTkWM7J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.651667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}